Project context:

This repository implements the Camagru project from the 42 school curriculum.

The goal is to build a small web application that allows users to capture or upload images and combine them with predefined overlays.

Technologies used:
- PHP (standard library only)
- HTML
- CSS
- Vanilla JavaScript

External frameworks and libraries are not allowed.
